          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Quapaw Tribal Landowner Settlement Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of the Interior to make FY2021 payments to members of the Quapaw Tribe of Oklahoma in accordance with the January 2020 recommendation of the review panel of the U.S. Court of Federal Claims.</p>]]>
